•   f.(n+1) = f.n ↑ a.n

⚠    n ∈ [0,N)

⊩   f.(n+1)

=   Definition of f

    ⚠    n+1 ∈ [0,N]

    ( n : n ∈ [0,N] : ↑( i : 0 ≤ i ≤ n-1 : a.i ) ).(n+1)

=   λ comp

    ↑( i : 0 ≤ i ≤ (n+1)-1 : a.i )

=   Arithmetic

    ↑( i : 0 ≤ i ≤ n : a.i )

=   Split-off term

    ↑( i : 0 ≤ i ≤ n-1 : a.i ) ↑ a.n

=   Definition of f

    ⚠    n ∈ [0,n]   -- f.n

    ⚠    n ∈ [0,N)   -- a.n

    f.n ↑ a.n

■